 2010-10022010-08-04,  ,  ,  AAFC, 
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - 2010 Prairie Excess Moisture Initiative
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to producers in the Prairie Provinces who were unable to seed a crop or had their crop flooded out as a result of excess moisture in the spring/summer of 2010 through a contribution under the federal component of the 2010 Prairie Excess Moisture Initiative.
